meta.githubCommitMessage:
Fix multiple bugs and improve build configuration

- Fix incorrect import path in hero-section.tsx (MediaPlaceholder)
- Fix type mismatch in mcp-content-generator.ts by casting category to MCPServerCategory
- Fix rehype-pretty-code callback signatures (onVisitHighlightedChars, added id parameter)
- Install missing shiki dependency for rehype-pretty-code
- Remove deprecated typescript.ignoreBuildErrors from next.config.mjs
- Remove deprecated swcMinify option from next.config.mjs
- Install and configure ESLint with next/core-web-vitals
- Update Next.js to 16.1.6 to fix security vulnerabilities (DoS and memory consumption)
- All TypeScript errors resolved, build now passes successfully

Co-authored-by: yaniv-apigene <yaniv-apigene@users.noreply.github.com>
